=== Testing Shell Tool Directly

[source,python]
----
from src.rag.rag_engine import RAGEngine

rag = RAGEngine()
rag.set_backend('ollama')

tests = [
    'SHELL: git status',
    'SHELL: git add .',
    'SHELL: git diff --staged',
    'SHELL: git log --oneline -3',
    'SHELL: git branch',
]

for q in tests:
    print(f'Q: {q}')
    resp = rag.generate_response(q)
    print(f'A: {resp}')
----

== Signaling an Issue

Before signaling an issue, please check that there isn't already a similar one in the bug tracking system.

Also, if this issue has been spotted in the CLI/TUI, please cross-check that it is still present with the current dependency set.
The issue may have already been corrected, but the changes have not been deployed yet.

